===INSTALL===

just for Unix-like(Mac, Linux):
+----------------------------------------------------+
|1.do make                                           |
|You can find a file 'Makefile',ok,do this:          |
|   $ make                                           |
|If have no accidents happend,It's ok!               |
|2.run duckweed                                      |
|   $ ./duckweed                                     |
+----------------------------------------------------+

then open a web_browser,input url '127.0.0.1:9000'(the
default port is '9000',you can see it in 'duckweed.h')
if you see 'duckweed works',that's great!whee...you are
lucky!

